VALUES
  ('social-worker-moex-01101', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列敘述何者正確？①有人會隱藏在團體裡造成「社會打混」（socialloafing）的現象  ②「社會', '["團體成員的增加必然可以使團體績 效相對提高", "團體成員付出較少的努力，而隨著團體移動前進的情況，稱之為「搭便車效益」 （freeridereffect）  ⑤團體裡有「搭便車」的人，後續難免會出現跟著打混或是做自己想做的事， 結果團體不成團體，稱之為「冤大頭效益」（suckereffect）  ⑥研究個人拉力與團體拉力，發現團 體拉力總是大過於個人拉力的總和", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01102', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關互惠模型（reciprocalmodel）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["在使用互惠模型過程，工作者扮演的角色是「中介者」（mediator）和「使能者」（enabler）", "工作者是「工作者與案主體系」的一部分，既被影響，也能影響他人", "工作者既不是針對案主，也不是為了案主，而是與案主一起工作", "工作者的自我揭露、熱誠、積極、知識等有助於其將專業權威表現在任務設計和問題解決"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01103', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '團體工作者於帶領非自願團體時，下列那些處遇較為適當？①培養幾位團體成員，促成更多正向', '["不讓成員有宣洩太多被迫害的負面情緒", "指出成員違法亂紀的行為並催化其改 變動機", "採用優勢觀點帶領團體", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01104', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一種團體最有可能有違GiselaKonopka所提社會團體工作倫理的界線？', '["心理劇團體", "冒險體驗教育團體", "強制親職教育團體", "失智症家屬支持團體"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01105', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '當社區的需求係由既有的標準或指標而來，係屬於下列何種性質的需求？', '["表達性需求", "感覺性需求", "規範性需求", "比較性需求"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01106', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-694fe135', 'sub-social-worker-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '若採用「社區教育模式」來進行社區工作，社區工作者會有下列那些作法？①鎖定某個特別貧窮', '["設置低階勞工或社區居民的成人教育服務", "藉由社區教育來提 高居民對社會參與動力", "針對社區既有迷思，舉辦公聽會來轉變其觀念", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d2632f5986ed", "answer_pdf_sha1": "86c7fc48aade", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作直接服務", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
